# InformationalEvent v1 — V2 single-rail refactor, plan §1.3.
# Reducer handler HandleInformationalEventV1 is a pass-through: it does NOT mutate
# DecisionState (LastAppliedSignalOrdinal + StepIndex are the only state deltas,
# applied by the shared reducer frame). It emits exactly one EmitEventTimelineEntry
# effect that reconstructs the full EnrollmentEvent from the payload keys defined in
# SignalPayloadKeys (eventType, source, message, severity, immediateUpload, dataJson).
# Missing optional keys use sensible defaults (severity=Info, immediateUpload=false).
# Any DataJson key is merged into the effect parameter dict so BuildDataDict in
# EventTimelineEmitter carries it into EnrollmentEvent.Data 1:1.
